reviewText: I had a set of these videos when my children were small and for some reason a couple of them are missing so I was able to replace them.
These series are usually very good and scripturally accurate however you do have to watch because their are a few of them that are not.
The image of all of the videos looks deceiving. It looks like you are ordering all of the videos that are seen. They should change the picture to only "Treasures in Heaven."
